programme.title: Layar Pesona: Geng Basikal
programme.desc: Memaparkan kisah kehidupan sekumpulan kanak-kanak iaitu Razlan, Roy, Remy, Kuzie dan Lim semasa zaman persekolahan hingga dewasa. Razlan dihantar oleh oleh ibu bapanya ke kampung untuk tinggal bersama atuk dan neneknya. Ibu bapanya ke luar negara selama dua bulan atas urusan kerja. Di kampung, Razlan mendapat kawan baru iaitu Roy, Remy, Kuzie dan Lim. Razlan seronok tinggak di kampung atuknya. Razlan melakukan banyak aktiviti bersama kawan-kawannya seperti bermain basikal, memancing, bermain bola dan sebagainya. Namun, Razlan tidak lama berada di kampung kerana perlu mengikut ibu dan bapanya ke London. Razlan berada dalam dilema. Pelakon: Nik Adam Mika, Aman Graseka, Olan Lam, Ily Mokhtar, Rosedah Amsar, Muhammad Hadi Putra, Muhammad Iskandar Zulkarnain, Muhammad Redzwan Adha.

Gara-gara mulut jahat mummy Camelia dan ditokok tambah oleh Miss Iliya, habis tular di Facebook bahawa Misi Dania aniaya anak orang. Tapi, Misi Dania ada bukti dia tidak bersalah! programme.title: Restu Ayah
programme.desc: Ibu bapa Azlan terlibat dengan kemalangan sewaktu pulang dari menghantar Azlan ke sekolah. Akibat kemalangan itu ibu Azlan meninggal dunia dan bapa Azlan buta sebelah mata dan patah kaki. Sejak peristiwa itu Azlan tidak dapat memaafkan bapanya. Azlan menuduh bapanya punca musnahnya kebahagiaan yang beliau kecapi selama ini.

programme.title: Huru Hara S14 Ep23
programme.desc: Di hoskan oleh Anas Ridzuan, Huru Hara kali ini pasti membuatkan anda terhibur sambil bergelak ketawa. Dalam episod ini kita santai santai bersama barisan artis yang terdiri daripada Aizuddin Bento, Amad Fadlin, Akmal Ahmad dan Xpose Band.

programme.title: Kandas
programme.desc: Seorang arkeologis bernama Amir dan seorang wartawan bernama Aina terjebak dalam kejar-kejaran dengan kumpulan samseng di hutan Perak setelah menemukan bangkai kapal terbang British. Selama melarikan diri, mereka menghadapi berbagai rintangan dan berangsur-angsur membangun hubungan yang erat. Di tengah petualangan itu, perasaan di antara mereka mulai berkembang, meskipun Amir masih mencintai Salina dan Aina memiliki hubungan dengan Wahid. Setelah melewati banyak cobaan, mereka berhasil keluar dari hutan. Wahid, yang telah menerima kenyataan kehilangan Aina, memutuskan untuk becuti di luar negara. Di saat yang sama, hubungan antara Salina dan Amir terus berkembang.

programme.title: The Gear Show S5 Ep2
programme.desc: Rancangan ini akan menampilkan kugiran pita hati yang akan membuat ulasan tentang barang barang yang digunakan untuk kugiran mereka.

programme.title: Anggun Mikayla Ep6
programme.desc: Perjalanan hidup Mikayla sentiasa bersimpang-siur dengan dugaan sejak dia mencelikkan mata birunya ke dunia. Status kelahirannya membuatkan dia seringkali menerima cacian penduduk kampung dan menjadi mangsa buli semasa kecil. Mekap adalah cara Mikayla menidakkan kewujudannya sendiri. Dia berselindung di sebalik rambut palsu hitam untuk menyorokkan rambut auburnnya serta mengenakan pelbagai jenis mekap untuk menggelapkan warna kulit kerana keinginannya untuk tampak Melayu. Siang, Mikayla bekerja sebagai jurumekap artis dan apabila malam tiba, dia menjelma sebagai pontianak. Pertemuan Mikayla dengan Idriz dalam satu insiden lucu telah mencipta satu hubungan aneh yang tidak bernama. Dalam diam, Idriz menyimpan rasa tetapi keinginannya terbatas kerana tanggungjawabnya pada keluarga. Jurugambar yang bekerja bersamanya, Asif yang suka mengusik Mikayla mulai tersedar yang usikannya sudah bertukar menjadi perasaan sebenar. Tetapi, dia terlajak memikat pelakon popular bernama Andria, sebelum tersedar tentang perasaannya terhadap Mikayla. Sedang Mikayla dalam keadaan celaru, lelaki dari masa silamnya, Aidan pula muncul kembali, menagih kemaafan kerana meninggalkan parut panjang di dahinya. programme.desc: Aileena sebenarnya anak angkat kepada Puan Katrina dan Tuan Haidar. Mereka menemui Aileena di dalam sebuah kotak yang ditinggalkan di tepi tong sampah. Pada masa tersebut, Puan Katrina dan Tuan Haidar baru dua tahun berkahwin. Melihat sahaja bayi perempuan yang comel itu, Puan Katrina langsung jatuh kasih dan meminta izin kepada suaminya untuk menjaga bayi itu. Aileena sentiasa didatangi mimpi mengenai seorang wanita gila berketurunan cina . Dalam mimpinya itu Aileena dipanggil anak dan dia sentiasa melarikan diri daripada wanita itu. adakah maksud tersirat disebalik mimpi itu?

programme.title: Anggun Mikayla Ep8
programme.desc: Perjalanan hidup Mikayla sentiasa bersimpang-siur dengan dugaan sejak dia mencelikkan mata birunya ke dunia. Status kelahirannya membuatkan dia seringkali menerima cacian penduduk kampung dan menjadi mangsa buli semasa kecil. Mekap adalah cara Mikayla menidakkan kewujudannya sendiri. Dia berselindung di sebalik rambut palsu hitam untuk menyorokkan rambut auburnnya serta mengenakan pelbagai jenis mekap untuk menggelapkan warna kulit kerana keinginannya untuk tampak Melayu. Siang, Mikayla bekerja sebagai jurumekap artis dan apabila malam tiba, dia menjelma sebagai pontianak. Pertemuan Mikayla dengan Idriz dalam satu insiden lucu telah mencipta satu hubungan aneh yang tidak bernama. Dalam diam, Idriz menyimpan rasa tetapi keinginannya terbatas kerana tanggungjawabnya pada keluarga. Jurugambar yang bekerja bersamanya, Asif yang suka mengusik Mikayla mulai tersedar yang usikannya sudah bertukar menjadi perasaan sebenar. Tetapi, dia terlajak memikat pelakon popular bernama Andria, sebelum tersedar tentang perasaannya terhadap Mikayla. Sedang Mikayla dalam keadaan celaru, lelaki dari masa silamnya, Aidan pula muncul kembali, menagih kemaafan kerana meninggalkan parut panjang di dahinya. Aidan yang kini sudah bergelar pelakon popular cuba memadamkan kenangan sakit mereka demi merebut hati yang dirinduinya itu. Tetapi, impian Mikayla hanya satu, berhadapan dengan masa silamnya dan mencantas kebencian mama. Cinta bukan destinasi yang diimpi. Namun, hatinya terus menjadi buruan oleh tiga orang lelaki.

programme.title: Jendela Hati Ep6
programme.desc: Zulkarnain pernah terkilan kerana familinya ada merancang untuk menjodohkannyadengan Farah, namun Farah pula dinikahi Lukman sebagai ganti tikar. Lukmanmempertikaikan tindakan Farah yang menghilangkan diri selama beberapa hari tanpamemberitahunya. Farah membidas Lukman yang culas amanah sebagai suami.

programme.title: Sembang Selebriti S4 Ep2

programme.title: Dihatiku Ada Kamu Ep24
programme.desc: Rian kembali bersikap dingin pada Adif. Adif tak faham kenapa. Rian pergi jumpa Fitrin lagi dan nak tahu tentang hubungan Fitrin dengan Adif. Rian pulang dengan sedih seperti dia ditipu oleh Adif sekali lagi. Afeeq tanya Fitrin jika dia sudah cerita semua. Fitrin yakin Rian akan kembali. Afeeq rupanya berpakat dengan Fitrin untuk pisahkan Rian dengan Adif. Rian bertemu Indri selepas dipujuk tentang kerjasama. Adif dan Farhan tiba di butik, tapi Rian sudah keluar jumpa Indri. Adif cemburu. Rian luang banyak masa dengan indri yang bantu design baju. Satu malam dah lewat, Afeeq datang ke butik dan Adif juga datang. Masing masing terkejut lihat Rian yang nak terjatuh, dipeluk oleh Indri.

programme.desc: Untuk episode kali ini, Chef Kim akan berkongsi dengan penonton, cara menyediakan Bebola Daging Marinara & Kek Cawan Coklat.

programme.title: Ong Bak 3
programme.desc: Kisah pahlawan Tien, yang telah ditangkap oleh panglima perang yang kejam Tuan Rajasena. Tien melarikan diri daripada cengkaman Rajasena, pulih daripada kecederaannya yang melumpuhkan dengan bantuan Guru Bua, dan kembali untuk berhadapan dengan Bhuti Sangkha, yang telah menggantikan Rajasena sebagai penjahat utama.

programme.title: The Hollow One
programme.desc: Rachel dan Anna pulang ke rumah dua tahun selepas kematian ibu mereka, dan dapati bandar itu ditinggalkan dengan rumah mereka dalam keadaan kacau dan kotor. Apabila Rachel mula mengalami halusinasi mengenai ibu mereka yang sudah meninggal dan sesuatu artifak purba, petunjuk-petunjuk menakutkan mula terbongkar mengenai masa lalu keluarga mereka.

programme.title: Gemersik Berbisik Ep1
programme.desc: Kimi dan Tasya ke Terengganu buat kajian tentang Lagu Jong Jong Inai. Berkenalan dengan Daniel yang turut ke Terengganu mencari keluarganya.Semasa buat kajian Jong Jong Inai, diganggu oleh hantu Suzana.

programme.title: Cinderella's Curse
programme.desc: Cinderella, dalam keadaan terdesak, memanggil ibu pari-parinya melalui sebuah kitab kuno yang terikat dengan kulit manusia, dengan harapan untuk menuntut keadilan dan membalas dendam terhadap ibu tiri dan kakak tirinya yang sentiasa menyeksa serta menindasnya tanpa henti.

programme.title: Terowong Ep9
programme.desc: Ini bertajuk "Cantik" memaparkan adegan Nani menjadi igauan Yusry yang tertidur di pejabat. Jeritan Yusry yang ternampak Nani sebagai hantu memeranjatkan rakan-rakannya yang lain. Nani yang juga mendengar jeritan tersebut memarahi Yusry kerana mengatakan dia sebagai hantu. Sejak dari peristiwa tersebut Yusry mula tergilakan Nani yang kelihatan bertambah cantik. Perkara ini menyebabkan Sidah iri hati. Bagi Nani beliau telah berjaya menjadi cantik dengan menggunakan khidmat bomoh Tok Mok dengan memakaikan beliau susuk. Sidah yang tidak puas hati dengan kecantikan Nani menemui Bomoh Tok Mok. Beliau diberitahu pantang larang bagi orang yang memakai susuk. Nani kena banyak berpantang terutama mesti dengar cakap pendamping yang telah sisyaratkan oleh bomoh Tok Moh. Setelah pantang larang tersebut dilanggar oleh Nani serta dan menyebabkan wajah Nani kembali menjadi hodoh seperti asal.

programme.title: Terowong Ep10
programme.desc: Mengesahkan Taufik pulang kerumahnya setelah seminggu bertugas di luar. Isterinya Ruzi melayangnya dengan baik dan Taufik memang sayangkan isterinya. Namun setelah dia kembali bertugas di pejabat rakan-rakannya mengucapkan takziah di atas kematian isterinya. Taufik hairan dan mereka memberitahu kepada Taufik bahawa isterinya telah meninggal dunia akibat kemalangan di terowong. Taufik tidak percaya dan rakannya Mirul membawa Taufik ke terowong. Taufik pulang ke rumah terus dilayani isterinya Ruzi. Mirul bersama Fina datang mengendap dan melihat Taufik cakap bersendirian. Mereka percaya Taufik diganggu oleh Syaitan. Mirul bersama Fina menemui Bomoh mohon pertolongan untuk menyelamatkan rakannya. Darah binatang yang diberikan oleh bomoh dicurahkan pada ayam hutan yang dihidangkan oleh Taufik untuk isterinya Ruzi. Setelah memakan makanan tersebut, Ruzi meraung kesakitan dan hilang dari pandangan mata.

programme.title: Terowong Ep11
programme.desc: Ini mengisahkan Joe dan Lan berkelah di kawasan berhampiran dengan hutan. Pada malam hari Joe bermimpi menemui Puteri Bunian. Igauan Joe menyebabkan Lan tersedar dan meminta Joe melupakan perkara tersebut. Lan memberitahu Joe yang mereka akan kembali pada keesokan harinya walau bagaimanapun, Joe ingin meneruskan pengembaraan di hutan tersebut dan Lan terpaksa mengikutnya. Sekali lagi Joe ternampak Puteri Bunian dan Joe mengikuti jejak langkah Puteri Bunian serta diikuti oleh Lan. Kehadiran Joe dan Lan didunia orang Bunian menyebabkan Pahlawan Daik marah kerana Pahlawan Daik mempunyai perasaan untuk memperisterikan Puteri Bunian. Pahlawan Daik merancang untuk membunuh Joe dan Lan, walau bagaimanapun muslihat Pahlawan Daik diketahui oleh Puteri Bunian, Puteri Bunian bertindak membebaskan Joe dan Lan pulang ke alam nyata

programme.title: Terowong Ep13
programme.desc: Bertajuk "Kain Kapan" menceritakan Hadi seorang kontraktor yang tinggal bersama ibu dan isterinya Kamila dan Hadi telah meminta pertolongan seorang bomoh untuk menentukan perniagaannya maju dan boleh mendapatkan projek yang banyak serta berlipat ganda. Bomoh tersebut telah memberikan beliau seekor Pocong untuk membantunya menjadi kaya raya. Oleh kerana terlalu sibuk dengan perniagaannya, kadang-kala Hadi terlupa memberi makan kepada Pocongnya hingga menyebabkan Pocong tersebut mengganggu ibu Hadi. Ibu Hadi menyangkakan isteri Hadi yang membela hantu Pocong tersebut, justeru itu ibu Hadi telah meminta bantuan seorang Ustaz untuk menghalau Pocong tersebut. Ustaz telah berjaya menghalau Pocong tersebut, walau bagaimanapun Pocong tersebut telah berjanji bahawa dia akan merasuk dan masuk ke dalam tubuh Hadi.

programme.title: Barajiwa Ep2
programme.desc: Uzair menyerang Madi dengan ganas. Madi dimasukkan ke hospital dalam keadaan koma, Uzair dihantar untuk pemulihan. Uzair menumpukan perhatian kepada SPM. Dia pergi untuk melindungi Ajeeb daripada Hatta yang membawa kepada lebih banyak pergaduhan. Imran membalas dendam terhadap Uzair dengan memanipulasi Asyikin untuk menjadi GRO.

programme.title: Abang Long Fadil 1
programme.desc: Abang Long Fadil, seorang lelaki yang sentiasa berangan bahawa kehidupannya seperti seorang gangster. Namun, apabila sahabat baiknya, Malik, dimasukkan ke penjara, keadaan menjadi lebih huru-hara, dan angan-angannya mungkin tidak jauh daripada realiti.

programme.desc: Apabila tiada apa yang boleh dilakukan untuk pesakit Insomnia Fatal Familial di hospital, seorang pelajar perubatan telah menyuruh abangnya dipindahkan ke kemudahan rahsia di ruang bawah tanah untuk rawatan alternatif.

programme.title: Ong Bak: Muay Thai Warriors
programme.desc: Apabila kepala patung yang suci di sebuah kampung dicuri, seorang ahli seni mempertahankan diri pergi ke bandar besar dan mendapati dirinya mengambil dunia bawah tanah untuk mendapatkannya.

Berlumba-lumba di jalanan, kejar-mengejar, berkonvoi dan disaman oleh polis telah menjadi rasa masam dalam kehidupan mereka yang berkongsi minat yang sama.

programme.desc: Mengetahui bahawa bapanya telah berkahwin dengan seorang wanita sebayanya, Kanaya meninggalkan rumah, hanya untuk mengalami kemalangan yang menyebabkan dia di hospital berhantu.

programme.title: Tom Yum Goong 2
programme.desc: Kham enggan menjual gajahnya Khon kepada peniaga, Suchart Vilawandei yang bercadang untuk menjualnya kepada seseorang yang bekerja untuk gangster LC. Kham kemudiannya mendapati Vilawandei mati di rumahnya di Bangkok, dan dua anak saudaranya, ahli silat Ping-ping dan Sue-sue, menganggap dia bertanggungjawab. Semasa melarikan diri dari mereka, Kham bertemu rakan lamanya Sarjan Mark, yang memberitahu Kham tentang rancangan pengganas untuk mengganggu rundingan damai Kantana di Bangkok.

programme.title: Cinderella's Curse
programme.desc: Cinderella, dalam keadaan terdesak, memanggil ibu pari-parinya melalui sebuah kitab kuno yang terikat dengan kulit manusia, dengan harapan untuk menuntut keadilan dan membalas dendam terhadap ibu tiri dan kakak tirinya yang sentiasa menyeksa serta menindasnya tanpa henti.

programme.title: Araf 5
programme.desc: Mengisahkan tentang seorang wanita muda yang mendapati dirinya dalam mimpi ngeri yang mengerikan ketika cuba menyara keluarga bekas teman lelakinya yang membunuhnya. Zeynep, seorang wanita muda, kecewa apabila dia mengetahui bahawa bekas teman lelakinya Kadir membunuhnya dengan cara digantung. Mengucapkan takziah kepada keluarga Kadir, Zeynep memutuskan untuk tinggal bersama mereka selama beberapa hari untuk menyara mereka atas desakan ibu Kadir. Bagaimanapun, tiada apa yang dilihat di dalam rumah itu menggambarkan kebenaran. Dalam proses ini, Zeynep mengetahui tentang kematian Kadir daripada entiti yang menghantui rumah itu. Diseret ke dalam pusaran, Zeynep mendapati dirinya di tengah-tengah Api Penyucian, tempat antara dua alam.

programme.title: Adnan Sempit 3
programme.desc: Menyaksikan Adnan berkahwin dengan cinta zaman kanak-kanaknya, Nadia, manakala Bobby pula berkahwin dengan Wawa. Adnan juga semakin mahir menguruskan perniagaannya sendiri. Walau bagaimanapun, kedua-dua pasangan ini segera menyedari bahawa perkahwinan bukan sekadar berkongsi rumah bersama seseorang, tetapi lebih daripada itu.

programme.title: Perempuan Bergaun Merah
programme.desc: Sejak sahabat baiknya hilang, hidup Dinda berubah menjadi mimpi ngeri apabila satu roh jahat yang berupa wanita berbaju merah menghantui dirinya. Dinda terancam bukan hanya oleh roh jahat itu, tetapi juga oleh individu yang cuba menyembunyikan kejadian malam kehilangan sahabatnya.

programme.title: Jwanita
programme.desc: Jwanita (Maya Karin) yang sakit mental dan didera oleh Ibu / Dukun (Umie Aida) dan bapa angkatnya (Radin Intan), yang mengamalkan ilmu hitam. Jwanita kemudian bertemu dengan Farhan (Bront Palarae) yang menjaganya selepas dia membunuh kedua ibu bapa angkatnya dalam satu peristiwa tragis.

programme.title: Din Tiger Ep3
programme.desc: Din Tiger berusaha mencari kebenaran di sebalik kematian isterinya, tetapi keadaan bertambah rumit akibat penyelewengan yang dilakukan oleh Anat terbongkar.

programme.title: Barajiwa Ep3
programme.desc: Apabila Uzair pulang ke rumah untuk bersama adik dan ibunya, dia dihalau oleh ibunya yang tidak mahu dia tinggal bersama mereka. Uzair mendapattahu bahawa Ashikin telah disimpan oleh Imran dan dia pergi untuk menyelamatkannya. Apabila Ashikin menyuruh melupakannya, Uzair kecewa dan pergi ke bandar.

programme.title: Rampok
programme.desc: Seorang wanita bersenjata merompak bank dan menjadikan mereka yang berada dalam bank sebagai orang tebusan. Pihak polis berunding dan wanita tersebut bersetuju untuk melepaskan tebusan tanpa pihak polis mengetahui bahawa orang tebusan tersebut merupakan perompak dan rakan perompak itu sendiri.

programme.title: Bini-bini Ku Gangster
programme.desc: Manja dan Herry adalah sepasang suami isteri yang sangat romantik dan saling sayang menyayangi. Tanpa disedari oleh Herry, Manja adalah ketua kumpulan kepada sebuah geng gengster di Kuala Lumpur. Di pejabat,Herry kerap dibuli Mat Saja termasuk menyuruh Herry menggantikan tempatnya semasa ulangtahun perkahwinan Manja dan Herry yang ke2. Manja bengang lalu menghantar orang-orangnya memukul Mat Saja.

programme.title: Awoken
programme.desc: Apabila tiada apa yang boleh dilakukan untuk pesakit Insomnia Fatal Familial di hospital, seorang pelajar perubatan telah menyuruh abangnya dipindahkan ke kemudahan rahsia di ruang bawah tanah untuk rawatan alternatif.

programme.title: Binhi
programme.desc: Daniel dan Cynthia, pasangan muda dengan anak dalam perjalanan, mengalami masa sukar di Manila. Mereka kembali ke Baguio, tempat asal Daniel, untuk memulakan semula. Melalui kebaikan Alex, kawan Daniel zaman kanak-kanak yang kaya, mereka dapat tinggal di sebuah rumah besar, tanpa sewa; dan dia mendapat tawaran kerja juga. Segala-galanya seolah-olah jatuh pada tempatnya untuk mereka - atau begitulah yang mereka fikirkan - sehingga perkara aneh mula berlaku di rumah mereka.

programme.title: Balun
programme.desc: Mengisahkan tentang seorang pemuda, Hassan yang membuat keputusan untuk pulang dan menetap di kampung asalnya di Kampung Putra, Kamunting kerana ada beberapa persoalan dan perkara yang harus diselesaikan, di mana salah satu perkaranya adalah perihal tanah milik arwah ayahnya, Mustafa yang dicagarkan pada Orang Kaya Seman sebelum itu.

programme.title: Azura

programme.desc: Mancer knows his father Wah is intellectually challenged since young and has to take care of him after his mother left them. When Mancer discovers and finds solace in stand-up comedy, he learns that hardships provide the best comedic material - from his own school ridicule experience to pandemic woes, misery can fuel laughter!

programme.title: New Kung Fu Cult Master 1
programme.desc: Wu Dang Sects Zhang Chui Shans son, Zhang Wu Ji, finds himself accidentally embroiled in the fight for the Dragon Sabre. When he unwittingly learns the powerful martial arts skills from the Jiuyin scriptures, Wu Ji proceeds to help the Six Major sects fight against the corrupt government.

programme.title: Chilli Laugh Story
programme.desc: Coba is forced to work at home during COVID-19 and fights with his family every day. He decides to turn his mothers chilli sauce into a trendy commodity to keep his family occupied. With his mother, father and aunt making the chilli sauce together, the family sells it online and the business grows beyond their imagination.

programme.title: Kung Fu Mahjong 2
programme.desc: Fanny appears to be an ordinary housewife but is in fact a mahjong expert. Deeply in love with her husband, she loses to a seductive woman, Curvy, both on the mahjong table and in competing for her husbands love. With the help from her mahjong master, Fanny vows to take on Curvy in the Mahjong King tournament!

programme.title: Lonely Eighteen
programme.desc: Set in the 1980s Hong Kong, Elaine and her best friend Ying enter the entertainment industry hoping to change their fates from poverty. Ying soon becomes a popular porn star but Elaine is lost between being her true self and an actress. When show business declines after a decade, their choices lead them to two different paths in life.

programme.title: Treasure Hunt
programme.desc: A commercial director Peggy shoots an ad on a deserted island while some mysterious men with the treasure map are also there to hunt for the hidden Ming Dynasty treasures. However, the map is stolen by Star who lives on the island. Star and Peggy unveil the hidden treasures but end up being chased by the mysterious men

programme.title: The Ex-Files 4: Marriage Plan
programme.desc: Two brothers, Meng Yun and Yu Fei, are of marriageable age and are facing challenges in love. Yun dodges family pressure to marry after his breakup, while Fei and his girlfriend opt for a marriage cooling-off period to tackle marriage issues.

programme.title: Kung Fu Dunk
programme.desc: Shi Jie grew up in a martial arts school and possesses an extraordinary shooting skill. Street hustler Chen Li sees his talent and arranges for him to join a university basketball team. With his kung fu dunking skill, Shi Jie manages to win all college basketball matches, bringing him wealth and also strengthening his relationship with Chen Li.

programme.title: The Way We Are
programme.desc: Set in Tin Shui Wai, a marginalised satellite town, Kwai is a middle-aged widow who works hard in a neighbourhood supermarket to support herself and her son. They lead a mundane but fulfilling life. When an elderly woman who lives alone moved in to Tin Shui Wai, Kwai strikes up a friendship with her and helps her ease into a new life.

programme.title: VR Fighter
programme.desc: Bodyguard Long Wei has posttraumatic stress disorder after his wife's death. One day, he encounters Amy who works for a VR technology firm and is invited for a new product test. After the test, Long Wei becomes the firms VR fighter and dons the newly invented armour. However, as mysterious armed men break in, a fierce battle has just begun...

programme.title: Wu Kong
programme.desc: Set 500 years before the Monkey King Wu Kong wreaks havoc in the heavenly kingdom, the movie tells the story of how Wu Kong who, unwilling to bow to his own destiny, sets out to rebel against the gods.

programme.title: The Movie Emperor
programme.desc: Hong Kong megastar Lau Wai Chi aspires to win a film award. He teams up with director Lin Hao to make a film about rural China so as to win at the international film festival, and experiences local village life for the farmers role. This ends up in a series of hilarious events instead.

programme.title: Bodyguards and Assassins
programme.desc: On 15 October 1906, Chinese revolutionary leader Sun Yat Sen returned to Hong Kong to stage another overthrow of the Qing dynasty. Businessman Lee and Chinese Dailys Chief Chan arrange for five bodyguards to protect Mr Sun - these are all extraordinary fighters who are ready and up for fierce battles against the Qing assassination army.

programme.title: Golden Chickensss
programme.desc: Ah Kam is now a mama-san leading a team of young prostitutes to service the rich and famous, and she always aims to fulfil every clients needs. When Ah Kams ex-lover, a triad boss, encounters difficulties adapting to a new Hong Kong after his release from a long imprisonment, she helps him get back on his feet to lead a normal life.

programme.title: Flirting Scholar from the Future
programme.desc: Tiger, Lambert and Skinny Pig are massive fans of the movie, Flirting Scholar. One day, Skinny Pig who is an obscure inventor, puts together a movie time machine and accidentally sucks all of them into the movie of Flirting Scholar. The trio head off to Wah mansion to meet the maid Autumn can they find her and can they return to the present?

programme.title: Enter the Fat Dragon
programme.desc: Donnie Yen plays a Hong Kong police officer who is highly skilled in martial arts but balloons to more than 200 pounds after his fianc left him. His boss can only assign simple tasks to him like escorting a criminal to Japan, but can he complete it?

programme.title: Adventure of the King
programme.desc: The Ming Emperor Zhengde flees the palace to see the world after his mother orders him to marry an ugly princess. He disguises as a commoner and escapes with his advisors, but a gambling mishap causes them to part ways and Zhengde lost all his money. Phoenix, the owner of Lung Fung Inn, takes him in out of pity, and thus begins his new adventure...

programme.title: City Under Siege
programme.desc: When circus clown Sunny gets transformed into a super-powered mutant, he finds himself pitted against his fellow circus performers who were altered in the same accident, and who are now using their powers to wreak havoc around the city.

programme.title: We are Family
programme.desc: Struggling as an extra, Chi Kwong joins a rent-a-family company run by Carlos and aspiring actress Catherine, and rent themselves out as make-believe relatives. As they surrogate different families, they unravel the complexities of family relationships, forging deeper connections along the way.

programme.title: A Witness out of the Blue
programme.desc: The police suspects that a jewel thief, found dead in his unit with all stolen goods missing, is killed by his gang leader. They also found the crime to be related to a jewel robbery many months ago, with the robbers involved being killed off one by one. In this complicated case, the polices only witness is a talking parrot from the crime scene.

programme.title: The Way We Keep Dancing
programme.desc: This sequel of The Way We Dance features the plight of Hong Kongs grassroots performing artists as they fight against the governments plan to gentrify an industrial district where they settled in.

programme.title: Once Upon a Time in Hong Kong
programme.desc: This is a story of ICAC investigators fighting against rampant corruption in early 1970s Hong Kong. A police sergeant teams up with a triad boss to make billions of dollars in bribes. As a lawyer joins his friend in ICAC to investigate their collusion and fight against corruption, the battle between the righteous and the wicked has just begun.

programme.title: I Fine… Thank You… Love You
programme.desc: Pleng, an English tutor, helps her student to pass a break up message in English to her boyfriend Gym. Gym knows nothing about English but wants to win back his girlfriend from the US, so he asks Pleng to teach him. Boorish and a slow learner, Gym makes many hilarious mistakes when learning English and ends up falling for Pleng.

programme.title: The White Storm 3 Heaven or Hell
programme.desc: Hong Kong cop Billy works undercover in Suchat's drug cartel, while another undercover cop Wing successfully earns their trust in an incident and a brotherly bond is built among the three. When the police busts the syndicate, Suchat flees to the Golden Triangle with Billy and receives a tip-off about the betrayal within his circle of trust

programme.title: Better Days
programme.desc: In this Oscar nominee for Best International Feature Film, Nian faces relentless bullying from her peers as she prepares for her college entrance exam. Fate leads her to streetwise punk Bei, but before they can retreat into their own world, both are embroiled in a murder investigation that will change their lives forever.

programme.title: Crypto Storm
programme.desc: ICAC investigation officer Lok sets up a special team to investigate a corruption case involving a banks top executives use of cryptocurrency to manipulate the trading market. When the banks chairman is kidnapped and kidnappers demand ransom in crypto coins, Lok connects the dots and vows to hunt down the mastermind behind both crimes.

programme.title: The Rookies
programme.desc: An extreme sports lover accidentally gets involved in an illegal trading activity by international crime syndicates. Led by international special agent Bruce, he forms an amateur unit with a police officer, an inventor and a doctor to fight the crime syndicates together, leading to a series of thrilling and hilarious adventures.

programme.title: 97 Aces Go Places
programme.desc: Hao Shi becomes the new triad boss after his father is killed by the pretty swindler, Ling. While professional gunman Drunken Gun is tasked to help Hao Shi take revenge, Ling is hunted by gangster Lei, from whom she has conned 2 million dollars. In the process, Hao Shi and Drunken Gun accidentally arrest Lei instead...

programme.title: The Infernal Walker
programme.desc: Ting is an undercover police who infiltrates a triad and Tuen is a triad mole being planted into the police force. While Tang is tired of being an undercover cop, Tuen wishes to quit the triad and become a real police. When the triad boss sets a trap to uncover the moles' identity, the two must fight for themselves.

programme.title: The Grand Grandmaster
programme.desc: Ma Fei Lung, a Chinese martial arts grandmaster, lost everything after he is floored by a former female boxing champion, Chan Tsang. The relevant video was posted on social media and he became the laughing stock of everyone. To reclaim his reputation, Fei Lung challenges Chan Tsang to a rematch. Who will be the winner?

programme.title: Five Superfighters
programme.desc: A kung fu master and his three students lost everything after they are floored by a bully. To take revenge, the students find ways to learn from other kung fu masters and come back six months later to have a rematch with the bully on their masters birthday.

programme.title: Carry on Doctors and Nurses
programme.desc: At St. Morant Hospital, a harried but lovely administrator must deal with lusty interns, student nurses, a delirious surgeon, a dissection fiend, a criticizing Commissioner and gross negligence at regular intervals! This comedy is based on the hugely successful British Carry On! film series.

programme.title: The 82 Tenants
programme.desc: Continuing the success of the classic comedy House of 72 tenants, this sequel tells the stories of tenants living in an old building in Hong Kong who are forced to evict by the developers. Some tenants prefer to take the compensation while some resist the move. Will the acquisitions plan destroy the harmony of the neighborhood?

programme.title: Emperor Chien Lung
programme.desc: Emperor Chien Lung goes incognito to mix with his people and understand their needs. He encounters many strange things along the way, including being arrested and nearly beheaded. Who will save him?

programme.title: The Kid With A Tattoo
programme.desc: Young Bao Tong witnesses the brutal murder of his kung fu master by a vicious villain. A large eagle tattoo on Baos chest was spotted by the killer as he escapes. Can Bao escape from the killer?

programme.title: Spring Blossoms
programme.desc: Some of Shaw Brothers' biggest female stars of the 1970s share the screen in this tale of young love and interfering parents, starring Lily Li, Shu Pei Pei and Essie Lin Chia.

programme.title: Return to the 36th Chamber
programme.desc: The second film of the trilogy, Gordon Liu plays Zhou Ren Jie, a man who impersonates a monk in order to learn kung fu in Shaolin, and eventually creates his own Shaolin style of scaffolding kung fu.

programme.title: The Dancing Millionairess
programme.desc: Peter was a key dancer in a dance troupe and applied to be the chauffeur of a rich girl, Betty. When he is rumoured to be her lover, Betty is furious and goes undercover as a reporter to investigate the rumour. They fall in love in the process, and after putting Peter through many tests, they finally seal their love with a dance.

programme.title: Mercenaries From Hong Kong
programme.desc: Filmmaker Wong Jing produced Mercenaries From Hong Kong, his very first modern-day adventure drama. In the dramatic plot he wrote, he sends superstars Ti Lung, Chen Hui-min, Wang Lung-wei, Lo Lieh and Wang Yu on a deadly mission. The film's action sequences are all closely guided by three great kung fu choreographers, led by Tang Chia!

programme.title: Forbidden Tales of Two Cities
programme.desc: Li Han-hsiang wrote and directed this charming and fascinating comedy, Forbidden Tales Of Two Cities. The two cities in the picture are Macau, where a love quartet is a morally-unsound source for sexual entertainment; and Hong Kong, where a woman enters a gamblers apartment to find four shackles hanging from his ceiling to aid in kinky activities.

programme.title: One-armed Swordsman
programme.desc: Accepted to the Golden Sword School after his father sacrificed his life to save his master, Fang Kang is resented by his fellow pupils and decides to leave. His master's daughter challenges him to a fight and cuts off his arm. Fang masters the art of sword fighting with one arm and finds himself returning to the School to save his master again.

programme.title: Ode to Gallantry
programme.desc: In this surprisingly light-hearted "Venoms" martial arts adventure, a lone wanderer is repeatedly mistaken for someone else and drawn into a number of violent battles.

programme.title: Passing Flickers
programme.desc: This film is an amusing insiders look at the Hong Kong film industry and is based on Director Li Han Hsiangs popular newspaper column recounting his work at Shaw Brothers. The collection of some of his funniest and most surreal film musings of the era, filled with behind-the-scene asides, this is a must-see for any Hong Kong cinema aficionado!

programme.title: That Fiery Girl
programme.desc: The bandits of Hulu Valley slay the chief of the Mei Clan while searching for a treasure map. In retaliation, Chun from the Mei Clan infiltrates the bandit's fortress to map a way in for the authorities, but ends up falling in love with the bandit leader's daughter, Pearl. While Chuns plot is uncovered, he receives unexpected help from Pearl.

programme.title: The Mad Monk
programme.desc: The movie consists of four stories of the Mad Monk helping others, from saving a mother and daughter from crumbling walls, to helping hawkers deal with bullies, recovering stolen money for a young man and punishing a devious court official and his son.

programme.title: The Young Avenger
programme.desc: Liu seeks out Li to avenge his brothers death and loses an arm in the fight, vowing revenge ten years later. Li dies after asking his sister to send his daughter Bao Zhu to learn the Dragon Sword skill to avenge his death. Bao Zhu grows up to become a skilled swordswoman and meets Liu for the planned duel with her cousin Chen. Can she defeat Liu?

programme.title: Rose, Be My Love
programme.desc: Not a love triangle but a love 'rectangle', Rose, Be My Love is a romantic drama set on the eve of World War II that represents the high standards achieved by Shaw Brothers in both aspects of star power and technical polish.

programme.title: Crazy Shaolin Disciples
programme.desc: Three young kung-fu warriors from wildly different backgrounds become students of Shaolin at the same temple. These three warriors are: Royal Guard Lo Lieh, fleeing soldier, Lo Meng, and villager, Wang Yu.

programme.title: Twinkle Twinkle Little Star
programme.desc: A beautiful but ignorant woman is abducted by aliens but nobody believes her close encounter. While planning a suicide to prove herself, she meets a failed detective who is also planning his suicide. They change their minds about dying after finding each other and start to encounter bizarre adventures, before falling in love with each other.

programme.title: The Savage Five
programme.desc: A group of bandits flees with a stolen safe to a village where they oppress the villagers and force the blacksmith Wei to unlock the safe. Wei refuses and flees to report to officials, while heroes of the town emerge to fight the bandits.

programme.title: Legendary Weapons of China
programme.desc: Lei Kung, the leader of the Boxer Clan in Yunnan, dissolves the clan to save his disciples before going into self-exile. The Clan sends various assassins to kill him but failed. They then assigned Kungs brother Yong to find and kill Kung, leading to a battle between the two brothers.

programme.title: Tales of Larceny
programme.desc: Connecting all the antics of bosses, monks, beggars, and thieves is the slippery and sinuous efforts of three pickpockets so adept at their chosen skill that they can even trick three beauties of their underwear without missing a step.

programme.title: Moods Of Love
programme.desc: This Song Dynasty period piece about how far one would go for love (or lust) has two tales. The first involves a devilish magistrate who tries to tempt a Buddhist monk out of his self-professed celibacy by hiring a pretty prostitute. The second is the tragic tale of an exploited young girl who is forced to work in an unscrupulous couples brothel.

programme.title: Usurpers Of Emperor's Power
programme.desc: The last ruler of Tang, Li Yao is deposed by Chao Kuang-jun, the founder of the Sung Dynasty. Unfortunately his actions unleash a new plague - his brother Kuang-yi - on the courts and his people. The marauding Kuang-yi rapes and plunders. As more people get involved, it turns into a bloody battlefield of betrayal. It is up to upright officials like Li Lang to put an end to it. But can one man take on the imperial army?

programme.title: Whose Baby is in the Classroom?
programme.desc: Chen, a male teacher in an all girls high school, is stuck with a baby that isnt his and must take care of it. As he lives on the school grounds, the baby is a source of constant distraction and worry! Luckily, his class warms to the baby and helps him take care of it while he works his charm on Li Ching, an uptight teacher in the same school.

programme.title: Sunset
programme.desc: Teenage heart-throbs Ching Li and Paul Chin Pei come across like Annette Funicello and Frankie Avalon in the musical Sunset, a musical romp that plays similar to one of Hollywood's famous "Beach Party" movies. A car load of girls meets a car load of boys, and Ching and Paul ultimately fall in love. Yet the film takes an acrid twist and turns out to be more like a Shakespearian tragedy than a beach-babe party.

programme.title: The Dragon Creek
programme.desc: This wuxia murder mystery film talks about a young girl whose father was ruthlessly murdered during China's early republican era. She has a list of villains who have been plotting against her father and together with her elder brother, the young girl sets out on a journey to hunt down the secret serial killer.

programme.title: The Happy Trio
programme.desc: Ah Chiao, a village girl stranded in the city, befriends a kind-hearted tramp and a retired actor. They are poor but happy, though Ah Chiaos fortune change for the better when she becomes a singer. However, she soon learns that money cannot buy one happiness...

programme.title: The Golden Lion
programme.desc: The Golden Lion is a bandit with good martial arts skills and often robs from the rich to help the poor. He is ambushed and attacked by a gang one night but luckily found help from a master healer, who has to find a way to treat him while they are both being chased by the gang.

programme.title: The Pure and the Evil
programme.desc: Two teen girls, Rose and May, become close friends despite their different social backgrounds. The rich girl May moves to America but returns years later to see Rose, now a beauty queen and bar girl. Rose is immediately attracted to Fangs fianc and their relationship quickly deteriorates when Rose sets out to pursue him

programme.title: The Sword And The Lute
programme.desc: Gui Wu and his bride use the deadly weapon - Phoenix Lute to fight against evil, but the lute accidentally falls into the hands of bandits hoping to use it to take control of the province. Gui Wu must now fight to recover the lute and beat the bandits.

programme.title: The Tiger and the Widow
programme.desc: The Liu Chia-liang trained Hui Ying-hung was considered the top action martial arts female star in the 1980s. It is her martial arts abilities that Michelle Yeoh tries to emulate. In The Tiger and the Widow, Hui Ying-hung is somehow mixed up in a salt smuggling ring that stinks of missing persons and rotten dilemmas.

programme.title: The Thunderbolt Fist
programme.desc: A vicious Japanese judo expert wants to prove that Chinese are the sick people of Asia and sets out to sabotage and kill the best martial artists in dangerous tournaments. To save his son from this, the head of Ping Pai Boxing Institute sends him to the mountains to learn the powerful Thunderbolt Fist technique from master fighter, Red Butterfly.

programme.title: Hong Kong Nocturne
programme.desc: This joyous, raucous, & colorful tunefest showcases the little seen dancing talents of celebrated kung-fu swordswoman Cheng Pei-Pei, as one of 3 girls dancing their way to the top.

programme.title: The Hidden Power Of Dragon Sabre
programme.desc: Defeated villain Sung Ching Shu returns and starts a reign of terror, trapping a beautiful Mongolian Princess and mastering the "yin and yang combination" to become almost invincible. Only two swords held by two great swordsmen can stand in his way!

programme.title: All Hail King Julien Ep33
programme.desc: Close Encounters Of The Mort Kind - When Mort is abducted by "aliens", King Julien teams with Clover, Maurice and Hector to investigate why he's not the one being abducted.

programme.title: All Hail King Julien Ep34
programme.desc: The Butterfly War - King Julien declares a war against butterflies to raise his kingdom's spirit, but when the village is destroyed he decides to hold a peace summit.

programme.title: All Hail King Julien Ep35
programme.desc: Fast Food Lemur Nation - Tired of waiting so long for his meals, King Julien introduces fast food to the kingdom, but the side effects are not what he expected.

programme.title: All Hail King Julien Ep36
programme.desc: Get Off My Lawn - When King Julien thinks he's a crime victim, he buys the village self-defense scorpions from a shady dealer, leaving everyone armed and dangerous.

programme.title: All Hail King Julien Ep37
programme.desc: Revenge Of The Prom - The gang joins King Julien at his Lemur School Reunion, but the party gets out of control when his old prom date, Karen, shows up for revenge.

programme.title: All Hail King Julien Ep38
programme.desc: Eye Of The Clover - Clover wants to follow in her Grandma Rose's footsteps and compete at the dangerous Tournament of Doom, but King Julien forbids her to attend.

programme.title: All Hail King Julien Ep39
programme.desc: Run For The Border - When King Julien hosts the ultimate party, his Boom Box breaks, the kingdom becomes too crowded and he builds a giant wall to surround the kingdom.

programme.title: All Hail King Julien Ep40
programme.desc: The All Hail King Julien Show - King Julien launches a new TV channel called Julien-Vision but quickly realizes that the kingdom only wants to watch a reality show of his own life

programme.title: The Adventures Of Puss In Boots Ep14
programme.desc: Pigs - Toby's ninja brother Brandt returns to San Lorenzo, and Puss agrees to help him reunite with his brothers to get them out of town.

programme.title: Not Quite Narwhal Ep14
programme.desc: Chef J's Tale - Chef J tells a tale about unicorns sailing in ships on clouds in search of Unicorn Land.

programme.title: Dew Drops Diaries Ep14
programme.desc: Dew Drops Day Off / Up All Night - When the Dew Drops have the day off, they discover their families still need their help when theyre not around. / Harper needs a good nights sleep before her first day of Cooking Camp. But when an overtired Nicholas keeps her awake, the Dews must help keep Nicholas quiet, even if it takes all night.

programme.title: Dragons: Rescue Riders Ep14
programme.desc: Grumblegard, Part 2 - The Rescue Riders plan to team up with the Slinkwings when an angry Grumblegard threatens Huttsgalor. But their old enemies may be up to new tricks.

programme.title: Go, Dog. Go! Ep14
programme.desc: Raiders of the Lost Bark / Slow, Dog. Slow! - When Tag and Scooch break Gilbers ancient Golden Slipper, they embark on an adventure to a secret cave to retrieve the matching slipper. \ For community outreach day, the Race Cadets are paired with an elderly resident of Pawston. It's Tag and Scooch's job to take old dog Leo around town for a day of slow, relaxing activities. But when Leo wants to kickbarx, row and skydive, Tag and Scooch try their best to keep up.

programme.title: The Epic Tales of Captain Underpants Ep42
programme.desc: Captain Underpants And The Senseless Torment Of The Space Toilet - Inspired by their favorite TV show, George and Harold along with Principal Krupp blast off to outer space, where an angry toilet awaits.

programme.title: The Epic Tales of Captain Underpants Ep43
programme.desc: Captain Underpants And The Abandoned Artifact Of The Absentee Aliens - After George and Harold learn the truth about their mission, Dupe Licitous enlists the entire crew in a quest to repair a rogue satellite.

programme.title: The Epic Tales of Captain Underpants Ep44
programme.desc: Captain Underpants And The Hazardous Hysteria Of The Hangry Hypnosinger - Everybody on the spaceship has been cryogenically frozen for three months everyone, that is, except Krupp, who's wide awake and happily in charge.

programme.title: Dragons: Riders of Berk Ep10
programme.desc: Heather Report Part I - Hiccup and the gang befriend a beautiful stranger who has a dangerous secret.

programme.title: Dragons: Riders of Berk Ep1
programme.desc: How to Start a Dragon Academy - Hiccup is given the responsibility to integrate dragons into the village of Berk and must contend with his rowdy friends, unruly dragons and an upset village elder.

programme.title: Dragons: Riders of Berk Ep2
programme.desc: Viking For Hire - Now that dragon-killing is no longer necessary, Hiccup tries to find a new job for Gobber the Blacksmith, but the task proves harder than expected.

programme.title: Boss Baby: Back in the Crib Ep62
programme.desc: The Great Medieval London Fire 1135 - Boss Baby and Tina reject the 5%er system that says the cuter you are, the more love you deserve. Teaming up with the Uncuddleables, the team tries to take down the system from within, forming a resistance of the eight department heads of Baby Corp in the hopes of changing the way we look at Baby Love forever.

programme.title: Boss Baby: Back in the Crib Ep63
programme.desc: Untitled Templeton Project - Fired from Baby Corp and trying to build their own business, Boss Baby and Tina waste all their startup funds immediately, requiring a loan from Banker Baby Benny. In order to receive their seed money and get their company rolling, they have to rebuild the towns faith in a baby who made everyone miss a huge sporting even (and they have to do it on a very limited budget)

programme.title: Boss Baby: Back in the Crib Ep64
programme.desc: Puppy Love - Unable to land baby clients, Boss and Tina take in a naughty little puppy as a side hustle, trying to earn a little extra scrap. But once they discover the dogs in the neighborhood are stealing for a puppy trainer named Becker, the mission gets much bigger, and our team is forced to earn a little Puppy Love for once.

programme.title: Kung Fu Panda: The Dragon Knight Ep10
programme.desc: The Knight's Fall Part 1 - Po and Blade rush to warn the Emperor about the weasels, but he has Po arrested and Colin captures Blade, revealing that she was never a knight. Thrown in a cell, Po reunites with Rukhmini and Mr. Ping, and he copes with the truth about Blade as they break out. Po fights Klaus and Veruca but is outmatched. Blade defeats Colin and hurries to help Po but is too late.

programme.title: Kung Fu Panda: The Dragon Knight Ep11
programme.desc: The Knight's Fall Part 2 - Blade tells Po the truth about Alfie. The group chases after Klaus and Veruca in an epic snowy mountain chase, culminating in Po saving Blades life as the weasels take off with the gauntlet and the whip. Rukhmini reveals that she actually has the real whip in her staff, and she knows where to go to get the next one: India.
